        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"ourStoryBox\" >\n\n<div class=\"storyContentBox\">\n<h3 class=\"philosophyTitle\">Why <i> We Started</i></h3>\n<p class=\"philosophyContentBox\"  >\nAs someone who's always valued simplicity, I found it ironic that the very things designed to organize our lives were often causing more chaos. That frustration turned into inspiration.  <br /> <br />\nWhat if our everyday essentials could be both beautifully minimal and incredibly functional? What if we could create products that actually made life easier, not just prettier?   <br /> <br />\nThis wasn't just about making another bag brand – it was about reimagining how we interact with the things we carry every day.\n\n</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0924/0677/6122/files/1_46ab4c05-fe73-455b-a21b-bc967b7ee908.png?v=1740429425\" />\n</div>\n</div>",
